If your Cat has a choice, they will prefer to drink running water as their instinct tells them that running water is clean! As a bonus, running water is more oxygenated and creates a perfect way for your cat to drink more water, a key for better health.
CatH2O features many aspects that make a great fountain, it also includes a bonus Dental Care feature to help improve your Cat’s dental health.

Provide your cat with fresh and clean water at all times.
Save time and hassle from refilling the water bowl every day.

The bowl is detachable and easy to clean.
